ActFirearms Act
SubjectFirearms Records Regulations (Classification)
PrecisFIREARMS RECORDS REGULATIONS (CLASSIFICATION) in order to require the Registrar of Firearms to keep a record of every classification determination made by them, and to prohibit the amendment of those records one year after the day on which the record is made.
